The '''Indu GNN bureau''' was a branch of the [[Galactic News Network]], based on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Indu San/Legends|Indu San]]. The bureau took local [[Media/Legends|news]] stories and transmitted them via [[Courier droid/Legends|courier newsdroids]] to the rest of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The Indu GNN bureau covered the [[Assassin/Legends|assassination]] of the [[Indu Council]]'s chief [[council]]or, [[Shek Barayel]].<ref name="Kella Rand, Reporting...">{{JournalCite|6|Kella Rand, Reporting...}}</ref>

